request.description:
Used in Home Page

The following components are received through this API

- Target id for "Gift Card" menu - used for routing
- count in cart / wishlist (for Authenticated users)
- Currency drop down
- Banner information (Main banner / advertisement banner / New arrival)
- Product categories - for the section of "Browse By Category"
- Flash Sale - If there are content then only shows the flash sale category in home page
- New arrivals - Banner to be taken from "Banner":\[\] object. The products to be listed will be within "newArrivals" \[\]
- Collections: always take the first two collections to show
- Settings - includes information for footer
